# TDD Workflow Demo
# Records: /tdd slash command showing test-first development

Output images/tdd-workflow.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Shell "zsh"

Type "claude"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "/tdd Add a function that validates email addresses and returns structured errors"
Enter
Sleep 15s

Type "q"
Sleep 1s
